<p>Sure. My name is David Zhang. I first stepped into computing as a Computer Science student at Newcastle University, where I studied from fundamental topics like database, to more cutting-edge areas like computer vision and AI. Through exploring such a broad range of disciplines, I not only discovered my passion in software development, but aslo built a strong CS foundation with a First-Class degree as a top 3% graduate.</p>
